{"tid":2023751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎同我推行動Post呀","createTime":"2020-05-19T07:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T07:28:55.000Z","uid":113441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a84f0eb6920bf55a2e60694d3ff2e59b57e5e6d2","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQTrvcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQTrvcd.jpg&h=214a0acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國歌法近，我地要出動既時刻都不遠矣。<br />\n<br />\n一齊為手足打氣加油，不論你係邊一個光譜既人，作為香港人只有一個理念!<br />\n<br />\n就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎起你既手機一齊出一分綿力，分少少元氣比我，準備面對呢個垃圾政權。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約定你，未來見。"},{"pid":"7173938381558de13874608508f5aadf2951ca0d","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9b25f37e9157e794be808b53702010e7169ebb7c","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:58:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"b85868dbb1de54a455bc3ee31b4ce46c5c7222d7","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"8fefbb2bc10358d4aa7d556c6bc707c110d6f6d2","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9bfb369d77c8edba4781512fe13ecc47faa49e2c","tid":2023751,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pi